Realni chisla

float , double - IEEE754

float 32bit - 4byte
double 64bit - 8byte

float - 1bit znakov
8 bit - eksponent
23 bit - mantisa

cifrite sled zapetaqta v mantisata 
stepenta na chisloto v exponentata

double - 1 bit znakov
11 bit - eksponenta
52 bit - mantisa

a && 0 = 0
a && 1= a
a || 0 = a
a || 1 = 1
a ^ 0 = a
a ^ 1 ! a

a >> n = a / 2^n

a << n = a * 2^n

mask

1. Check bit : !! (mask & 1<<bit )

2. set bit : mask = mask | (1<<bit)

3. clear bit :mask= mask & ~(1<<bit)











